metadata.name: Ada's last song
metadata.description:
Prompt: A cyborg in a cryogenic environment whose soul is leaving his body and floats around and merges with a nebula of energetic colors'

Medium: Digital render 2048x2048, 3D experience to be enjoyed on PC or VR, and story/poem performed by me.

Why did you choose this prompt? -- Always been fond of Sci-Fi and found the idea of a cyborg thinking about life and death as something interesting

AI used? -- no

I tried to stay as true to the original prompt as possible. I changed the gender since i felt it fitted better to my theme. Her name is Ada 49 and you can read her story on my submission page along with her song/poem. Deeper insight into my creative process that lead to this result are there too. Please read it! It contains blog posts, video and detailed information you need to read in order to understand and fully appreciate the scope of this art.

VERY IMPORTANT! Visit this page to learn all about this art
[Submission page](https://www.g3n3zis.com/humanitysubmission)
